According to Market Surveys of America, an independent survey company, the center provides the best service when it comes to hearing aids.¬†¬†This is the 6th time that Warren Center has earned the honor.¬†¬†Winners are the result of tallied public ballots taken throughout the Bangor area for the small business community.

Warren Center has provided speech and hearing services to the greater Bangor area for 50 years.¬†A service of Penobscot Community Health Care,¬†¬†the Warren Center has Audiologists and Speech-Language Pathologists providing services Monday-Friday 8am-5pm and is open to new patients. Warren Center is conveniently located at 992 Union Street, Bangor, on PCHC‚Äôs main Bangor campus.¬†¬†To learn more about PCHC and the Warren Center, please visit¬†<a href="http://www.pchc.com/">www.PCHC.com</a>.";s:10:"post_title";s:52:"Warren Center Named Area‚Äôs Best Hearing Aid Center";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:49:"warren-center-named-areas-best-hearing-aid-center";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-09-20 10:48:26";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-09-20 14:48:26";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:26:"http://www.pchc.com/?p=490";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"493";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"5";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2013-08-15 10:09:35";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2013-08-15 14:09:35";s:12:"post_content";s:1246:"Pediatric Walk-In Care will be open and available to the community at Penobscot Pediatrics, 1068 Union Street, Bangor (near the Airport Mall) beginning August 19th. High-quality acute medical care, including urgent visits and treatment of non-emergency conditions, will be available for children Monday-Friday 7:30am to 7:30pm and Saturday, Sunday, and most holidays 9am to 4pm. <strong>Please join us for the grand opening of this new service at Penobscot Pediatrics on Monday, August 19th at 10am.</strong>
