Dr. Sandhu has a special interest in tropical medicine and returns to India each year where she continues to serve her patients there. Dr. Sandhu also has interests in Sports Medicine, Women‚Äôs Health, and Integrative Medicine, and is seeing patients at Penobscot Community Health Center; for an appointment please call 945-5247. Penobscot Community Health Center is open seven days per week and, in addition to family medical care, offers Walk-In Care, Pharmacy, Physical Therapy, and Mental Health Services.";s:10:"post_title";s:60:"Kernjeet Sandhu, MD, Joins Penobscot Community Health Center";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:58:"kernjeet-sandhu-md-joins-penobscot-community-health-center";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-09-20 10:38:14";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-09-20 14:38:14";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:26:"http://www.pchc.com/?p=499";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:11;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"944";s:11:"post_author";s:2:"10";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2013-10-21 09:00:06";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2013-10-21 13:00:06";s:12:"post_content";s:1071:"PCHC is happy to announce the arrival of its new, updated website!

